data.enText: a mixture of rain and snow
when it is sleeting , a mixture of rain and snow is falling from the sky

tr: partially melted snow (or a mixture of rain and snow)
precipitate as a mixture of rain and snow
example: If the temperature rises above freezing, it will probably sleet

value.def: Sleet is rain that is partly frozen.

example.tran: 漫天大雪、猛烈的冻雨和大风
